OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,FAn investigation into Russian-backed
OL,7,Fparcel bombs in the UK and Europe has
OL,8,Fidentified 22 suspects.
OL,10,FA number of parcels exploded in the
OL,11,FUK, Germany and Poland - one package
OL,12,Fcaught fire at a DHL depot near
OL,13,FBirmingham in 2024.
OL,15,FA 38-year-old Romanian man was
OL,16,Farrested by counter-terrorism police
OL,17,Fover the Birmingham fire and remains
OL,18,Funder investigation.
OL,20,FHe was apprehended after arriving on a
OL,21,Fflight to the UK at Stansted Airport.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
