FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,FBritish and European authorities now
OL,7,Fbelieve there was Russian involvement
OL,8,Fin the plot.
OL,10,FFour parcels were sent from Lithuania
OL,11,Fto addresses in the UK and Poland,
OL,12,FEuropean Union agency Eurojust said.
OL,14,FThe consequences could have been far
OL,15,Fworse if the devices ignited during a
OL,16,Fflight, officials fear.
OL,18,FA parcel sent through a sorting centre
OL,19,Fin Germany caught fire at Leipzig
OL,20,Fairport, just before it was loaded on
OL,21,Fto an aircraft.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,FInvestigators identified two test
OL,7,Fpackages that had been sent to the
OL,8,FUnited States and Canada, as well as
OL,9,Ftwo parcels in Amsterdam intended for
OL,10,Fthe same destinations.
OL,12,FAuthorities have identified 22
OL,13,Fsuspects in Lithuania and Poland
OL,14,Flikely to have been working on behalf
OL,15,FRussian military intelligence services.
OL,17,FTwo cases have now been sent to courts
OL,18,Fin Lithuania and Poland, with trials
OL,19,Fexpected to happen later in the year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,FThe suspected perpetrators were
OL,7,Frecruited from Russia, Latvia,
OL,8,FEstonia, Lithuania and Ukraine, and
OL,9,Fwere often in a "vulnerable socio-
OL,10,Feconomic situation", Eurojust said.
OL,12,FThey were recruited and given
OL,13,Finstructions through an online
OL,14,Fmessaging service, with tasks divided
OL,15,Famong them and payments made in
OL,16,Fcryptocurrencies.
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
