OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,FA UK government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Russia's ongoing hostile action puts
OL,8,Four national security at risk, which
OL,9,Fis why this Government has taken
OL,10,Fconcerted action to deter their
OL,11,Fhostility ` increasing defence
OL,12,Fspending, expelling intelligence
OL,13,Fofficers, sanctioning the GRU,
OL,14,Ftargeting their illicit finance, and
OL,15,Fensuring many of their proxies are
OL,16,Fbrought to justice.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,F"National security is the first duty
OL,7,Fof government, and our law enforcement
OL,8,Fpartners will continue to use the
OL,9,Frange of tools and powers available to
OL,10,Fthem to keep the British public safe."
OL,12,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Vicki
OL,13,FEvans of Counter Terrorism Policing,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The work of our European
OL,15,Fcounterparts has been truly remarkable
OL,16,Fand demonstrates the critical need for
OL,17,Fus to work across borders, as well as
OL,18,Fthe expertise of our colleagues
OL,19,Foverseas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,F"The strength of cooperation in this
OL,7,Fcase has led us to collectively
OL,8,Fidentify what we believe to be Russian
OL,9,Fmilitary intelligence involvement in a
OL,10,Fseries of incidents across Europe.
OL,12,F"Our investigation is ongoing, and we
OL,13,Fcontinue to liaise closely with
OL,14,Fpartners to ensure we're doing all we
OL,15,Fcan to keep the sector, and the public
OL,16,Fsafe.
OL,18,F"We have been clear and open about the
OL,19,Fincreasing levels of demand we're
OL,20,Fseeing relating to the activity of
OL,21,Fforeign states here in the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772831513
OL,3,CInvestigation into Russian-backed
OL,4,Cparcel bombs identifies 22 suspects
OL,6,F"For Counter Terrorism Policing this
OL,7,Fmeans more investigations, and our
OL,8,Fteams are working around the clock to
OL,9,Fidentify and disrupt a range of
OL,10,Factivity to protect the UK and the
OL,11,Fpublic from terrorism and other
OL,12,Fnational security threats."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@[O]
